headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Darden’s Q2 Earnings Call
summary: Darden’s second quarter saw a positive market reaction as the company delivered robust same-store sales growth and expanded its restaurant footprint. Management credited the success to value-oriented promotions at Olive Garden, such as the return of the "buy one take one" offer and expanded delivery options, which resonated with guests seeking affordability and convenience.
